{
  "stem": "10478.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I am afraid that people think, [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Bob ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Wallen ?] and guy is that, a name like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I never spoke about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Even my kids didn't know about it till I had a Jewish friend, here, Carl Goldstein.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He's also from Maastricht.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I always had close contact with him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he mentioned my name to the community [INAUDIBLE] in Ottawa, to-- to Mendel Good-- well-known.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they said, they promised me, say, listen, you should open your mouth now, because antisemitism is coming up again.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And people should know, witnesses, what happened, during the war time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They convinced me that it was time to speak up, yes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't like that they have the story.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I always had the feeling that they think that he's overdoing it, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that's why I keep quiet about it, yeah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, they found  it a fantastic idea.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were excited about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they listened to my stories, of course.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I got sick and tired of telling the same story all the time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So then I thought, well, if I can put it in a booklet, maybe they can actually read it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I found a ad in a-- in a magazine for seniors that someone was printing life stories, for seniors for the family.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I give them a call and asked for informations.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he came and told me what it would cost me if he did that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then a week later, he called me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My wife wants to see  you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She is a professional writer, and she wants to write a book about you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that way she started to write my book.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 118,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But that was later on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 119,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Janet Keith.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Janet Keith, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I visited her once or twice a week.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she didn't know the computer word processor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we did it on an old IBM.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But she just typed the whole story, what I told her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, a week later, she wrote it down a week later.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We re-read it, and we corrected it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so-- And what she did, of course, I give-- I supplied her with all the addresses for the Jewish people in Maastricht and also in Israel, and in Belgium.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she wrote them letters asking for their report.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that, she make, combined into one book.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, a couple of years, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was my story, yes, and the story of the people I helped, also, yeah.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I don't think that it-- I think they sold out now.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it is in the libraries, here, and also in the Jewish library in-- in community halls around here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1992, I believe, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, I do.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I keep in contact with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And usually with the Jewish new year, I send them a card or  a letter.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I get, with our Christmas, a letter back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They-- and then we've gone three times I went to Israel for a visit.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The first time, I went with a tourist group and let them know that I was coming to Israel.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we had a reunion in the Hilton Hotel in Jerusalem.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they were mad at me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said, now you go with a tourist group?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] You should have come to us, and we would have driven you around  here and seen something of Israel.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I had to promise them that I would come back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then even after I came back to Israel-- and they even were willing to pay for my trip.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, I can afford it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You don't need to do that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So the second time I went to Israel, I stayed at their place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they brought  me from  one place to the other.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I had a fantastic time there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And later on-- that was with my wife, together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And later on, I went by myself, for two times to Israel, I visit them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] I had my birthday a couple of weeks ago, and I got several calls from Israel.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So just part of a family, more or less, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And how many people are there in this extended family?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There, in Israel?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, roughly, there was about 100.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the contact I have with them is, of course, a lesser group, because some older people passed away, some moved away, I don't know where.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the majority I have contact maybe 30, 40, or something like that When I send cards to Israel, there's around 20 that I send every year to them.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Write letters and whatever, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
